BlockInput, Off
Return

; This one pastes the link with "Ink to Text" mode off, you have to highlight your expression if more than one word
F10::
BlockInput, On
Send, {AppsKey}
Sleep, 10
Send, {Up 5}
Sleep, 10
SendInput, {Enter}
Sleep, 10
SendInput, {Delete}
Sleep, 10
Send, ^v
Sleep, 50
Send, {Up 3}
Sleep, 10
